@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home";
}

<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="~/Images/SHMFlipped.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
                    <img src="~/Images/CodeTheWay Logo.png" alt="CTW Logo" />
                    <h1 class="font-weight-bold">Style. Design. Work.</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/Images/2019Pres.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption text-center">
                    <h1 class="font-weight-bold">Partnering</h1>
                    <p class="lead my-3">High Schools & Tech Companies</p>
                    @*<p class="lead my-3">Two years of high school students working for non-profits giving students real world job experience and letting students work collaboratively with eachother for a cause.</p>*@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/Images/ProjPres.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption text-right">
                    <h1 class="font-weight-bold">Contributing</h1>
                    <p class="lead my-3">To Real World Companies</p>
                    @*<p class="lead my-3">Multiple non profits that recieved more than $250,000 worth of technology services, which lets the human work get shifted to different important services. This aswell as sixty plus different students from multiple different schools having meaningful volunteer experiences, aswell as recieving scholarships and also having authentic work experiences recieved.</p>*@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>

<hr />

<h1 class="text-md-center py-2">Past Projects</h1>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="card-deck">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="~/Images/HeroesForHealthcare.jpg" class="card-img-top" />
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    <a href="/Home/Projects#2017" class="card-link stretched-link">Heroes for Healthcare</a>
                    <footer class="blockquote-footer">2017</footer>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="~/Images/LifeNavigatorsLogo.jpg" alt="" class="card-img-top" />
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    <a href="/Home/Projects#2018" class="card-link stretched-link">Life Navigators</a>
                    <footer class="blockquote-footer">2018</footer>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="~/Images/crc.png" alt="" class="card-img-top" />
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    <a href="/Home/Projects#2019" class="card-link stretched-link">Convergence Resource Center</a>
                    <footer class="blockquote-footer">2019</footer>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<h1 class="text-md-center">Testimonials</h1>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <blockquote class="blockquote text-justify">
            <p class="mb-0">The fundamentals that were learned here will make learning on the job much easier as we already know the main concepts of software development. Having this experience so early in our career is extremely valuable for our future is an experience I was very lucky to be a part of.</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer"><cite>Brett Koppelman</cite>, '18 BCHS</footer>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <blockquote class="blockquote text-justify">
            <p class="mb-0">This experience is close to priceless in value to me because I was able to see how much goes into a project. I was also able to take a peek into the professional realm where I may want to be in for my career. The connections I made will also help me in the future. I couldn't be more grateful for being able to take part in the first summer of Code the Way.</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer"><cite>Miriam Khan</cite>, '18 BCHS</footer>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <blockquote class="blockquote text-justify">
            <p class="mb-0">As the end of the summer quickly approaches, I can confidently say that my teammates and I have grown immensely in our knowledge of not only software development and the agile method but the business world as a whole.</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer"><cite>Ben Tan</cite>, '19 BCHS</footer>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col-md-12"><h1 class="mb-3">Students: Apply for the upcoming 2020 project season now!</h1></div>
    <div class="col-md-12">
        @Html.ActionLink("Apply Now", "Create", "StudentApplication", null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg", role = "button" })
    </div>
</div>
